566
00:35:08,070 --> 00:35:09,550
Suo Heng's Little Deity

567
00:35:09,550 --> 00:35:11,790
is the hottest topic on Moonlight now.

568
00:35:11,790 --> 00:35:13,230
Besides, it ranked the first

569
00:35:13,230 --> 00:35:15,430
