most anticipated novel ranking

570
00:35:15,430 --> 00:35:16,830
initiated by Yuan Yue's official website.

571
00:35:17,030 --> 00:35:17,870
Oh, God!

572
00:35:17,870 --> 00:35:19,900
This is the best news for new year!

573
00:35:19,900 --> 00:35:21,030
Exactly.

574
00:35:21,030 --> 00:35:22,990
Besides, Mr Xia has discussed with Mr Yang

575
00:35:22,990 --> 00:35:24,590
