576
00:35:24,590 --> 00:35:26,590
Mr Yang has agreed to let her stay.

577
00:35:27,230 --> 00:35:29,950
Then, will the comic section

578
00:35:29,950 --> 00:35:31,460
be put aside?

579
00:35:31,460 --> 00:35:32,390
Of course.

580
00:35:32,390 --> 00:35:33,780
The sections on Moonlight

581
00:35:33,780 --> 00:35:36,390
are only reserved for great work.

582
00:35:36,390 --> 00:35:38,940
Mr Liang will be pissed off.

583
00:35:39,030 --> 00:35:39,910
That is for sure.

584
00:35:40,750 --> 00:35:41,230
Let's go.

585
00:35:42,830 --> 00:35:43,830
Mr Liang,

586
00:35:43,990 --> 00:35:44,870
look at this.

587
00:35:45,510 --> 00:35:46,830
It's a new year,

588
00:35:46,950 --> 00:35:48,790
but there's not a good start.

589
00:35:49,590 --> 00:35:51,030
Suo Heng will publish her work,

590
00:35:51,230 --> 00:35:52,950
but the comic section will be removed.

591
00:35:53,070 --> 00:35:54,950
We added comic section

592
00:35:54,950 --> 00:35:57,630
just to increase the sales of Moonlight.

593
00:35:57,750 --> 00:35:59,070
But after what they've done,

594
00:35:59,070 --> 00:35:59,740
I...

595
00:35:59,740 --> 00:36:01,350
I've made a deal

596
00:36:01,350 --> 00:36:02,990
with those two cosplayers.

597
00:36:02,990 --> 00:36:05,710
What should I tell them now?

598
00:36:07,340 --> 00:36:08,270
It's hot, huh?

599
00:36:08,270 --> 00:36:09,230
It's hot.

600
00:36:09,230 --> 00:36:10,070
Look.

601
00:36:10,670 --> 00:36:12,670
You've always been so impatient.

602
00:36:13,270 --> 00:36:15,390
It wasn't even confirmed yet,

603
00:36:15,390 --> 00:36:17,110
why did you make a deal with them?

604
00:36:18,220 --> 00:36:20,150
Anyway, rest assured.

605
00:36:20,150 --> 00:36:22,350
Although they can't publish the comic
on Moonlight,

606
00:36:22,350 --> 00:36:24,430
they can always publish a book.

607
00:36:27,110 --> 00:36:28,710
Are you saying...

608
00:36:28,710 --> 00:36:30,030
Think about it.

609
00:36:30,190 --> 00:36:32,310
Another book will be released

610
00:36:32,310 --> 00:36:33,950
at the same time with Jiang Yu Cheng.

611
00:36:34,110 --> 00:36:36,190
Now this is a competition

612
00:36:36,190 --> 00:36:38,030
between Yue Yue and Xin Dun.

613
00:36:39,270 --> 00:36:41,750
How can a has-been shoulder our sales?

614
00:36:41,750 --> 00:36:44,390
Would the top management be so careless?

615
00:36:48,310 --> 00:36:49,140
You're right.

616
00:36:49,510 --> 00:36:51,110
I get it now, Mr Liang.

617
00:36:51,190 --> 00:36:53,030
I'll talk

618
00:36:53,030 --> 00:36:53,710
to the cosplayers

619
00:36:53,710 --> 00:36:56,350
about the details
of their autobiographies.

620
00:36:57,150 --> 00:36:58,150
Miao,

621
00:37:00,070 --> 00:37:01,670
listen to my advice.

622
00:37:02,710 --> 00:37:03,630
You

623
00:37:03,630 --> 00:37:05,540
should give your strength full play.

624
00:37:05,540 --> 00:37:07,270
Stay calm when a problem arises.

625
00:37:07,270 --> 00:37:08,510
Don't panic,

626
00:37:08,510 --> 00:37:09,630
don't get agitated.

627
00:37:09,750 --> 00:37:11,230
They're a has-been

628
00:37:11,230 --> 00:37:12,950
and a rookie,

629
00:37:12,950 --> 00:37:15,150
they have no influence.

630
00:37:15,430 --> 00:37:16,510
You...

631
00:37:18,190 --> 00:37:20,750
I get it now, I get it now.

632
00:37:23,950 --> 00:37:24,670
Mr Jiang,

633
00:37:24,670 --> 00:37:25,510
don't worry.

634
00:37:25,510 --> 00:37:27,550
You will make a great comeback.

635
00:37:28,030 --> 00:37:28,950
Great.

636
00:37:28,950 --> 00:37:31,390
I heard you and Zhou Chuan
are seeing each other.

637
00:37:32,060 --> 00:37:33,750
You knew.

638
00:37:33,750 --> 00:37:34,750
Yeah.

639
00:37:34,750 --> 00:37:36,630
That guy has always been thoughtless,

640
00:37:36,630 --> 00:37:37,630
if he pisses you off,

641
00:37:37,630 --> 00:37:39,310
just give him the long face.

642
00:37:39,630 --> 00:37:40,860
I will.

643
00:37:44,510 --> 00:37:46,830
What were you guys talking about?
You seem happy.

644
00:37:47,110 --> 00:37:49,630
Why should I let you know
our conversation?

645
00:37:49,630 --> 00:37:52,070
Don't you forget that she is mine now.

646
00:37:54,830 --> 00:37:56,430
Why did I hear the voice of Gu Bai Zhi

647
00:37:56,430 --> 00:37:58,670
when I called you the other day?

648
00:37:59,390 --> 00:38:00,830
Director Gu and you...

649
00:38:00,830 --> 00:38:02,310
They've broken up,

650
00:38:02,310 --> 00:38:03,950
but they haven't moved on.

651
00:38:03,950 --> 00:38:04,740
How's that?

652
00:38:04,740 --> 00:38:06,910
You're glad that you chose me, aren't you?

653
00:38:07,310 --> 00:38:08,430
That's not it.

654
00:38:08,430 --> 00:38:10,070
She was sick during Lunar New Year.

655
00:38:10,070 --> 00:38:11,780
I took care of her.

656
00:38:11,870 --> 00:38:12,910
Now I get it.

657
00:38:13,070 --> 00:38:13,860
My mum asked me

658
00:38:13,860 --> 00:38:15,790
if you went back to Shanghai with me.

659
00:38:15,990 --> 00:38:17,630
Right after I left
on the first day of Lunar New Year,

660
00:38:17,940 --> 00:38:19,140
you rushed back home

661
00:38:19,140 --> 00:38:21,230
just because she was sick.

662
00:38:21,990 --> 00:38:23,870
You also went to Zhejiang

663
00:38:23,870 --> 00:38:25,270
just because Chu Li changed her clothes.

664
00:38:25,270 --> 00:38:26,270
I...

665
00:38:28,750 --> 00:38:30,430
Mr Zhou Chuan.

666
00:38:31,430 --> 00:38:33,190
Shut the hell up.

667
00:38:35,870 --> 00:38:37,350
Let's go home and cook. Come on.

668
00:38:43,270 --> 00:38:44,510
Is it nice?

669
00:38:45,830 --> 00:38:47,510
It's nice,

670
00:38:47,510 --> 00:38:50,110
but I think the ending will be terrible.

671
00:38:50,590 --> 00:38:51,380
Based on internet sources,

672
00:38:51,380 --> 00:38:53,430
Yun Fei doesn't know anything
about early publication

673
00:38:53,430 --> 00:38:54,950
of the second book.

674
00:38:54,950 --> 00:38:56,350
Tens of thousands of comments

675
00:38:56,350 --> 00:38:57,750
are scolding Gu Bai Zhi
under her Weibo post.

676
00:38:58,870 --> 00:39:01,390
What does this have to do with Gu Bai Zhi?

677
00:39:02,150 --> 00:39:03,150
We never know.

678
00:39:03,270 --> 00:39:04,820
She always puts business first.

679
00:39:04,820 --> 00:39:06,030
However, this is the reason why

680
00:39:06,030 --> 00:39:08,340
she's the one
who could see Yun Fei's potential.

681
00:39:08,550 --> 00:39:09,660
I bet she won't do anything bad

682
00:39:09,660 --> 00:39:11,590
to Yun Fei right now.

683
00:39:13,830 --> 00:39:14,940
Stop reading.

684
00:39:14,940 --> 00:39:16,630
You got off work. Don't think about work.

685
00:39:16,870 --> 00:39:18,630
Come. Walk Er Gou with me.

686
00:39:18,630 --> 00:39:19,990
But the extra edition...

687
00:39:19,990 --> 00:39:21,670
Read it after we come back.

688
00:39:30,390 --> 00:39:31,510
Chu Li,

689
00:39:31,590 --> 00:39:32,910
listen.

690
00:39:32,990 --> 00:39:34,470
Mr Zhou Chuan's love letter

691
00:39:34,470 --> 00:39:36,870
has been forwarded
hundreds of thousands times.

692
00:39:36,870 --> 00:39:37,940
Look.

693
00:39:37,940 --> 00:39:39,870
The comments said

694
00:39:39,870 --> 00:39:42,390
The Gentle and Kind Mr Chuan

695
00:39:42,390 --> 00:39:45,470
will break so many hearts
when he gets romantic.

696
00:39:45,470 --> 00:39:46,670
A guy like him

697
00:39:46,670 --> 00:39:49,230
will win over any girl he likes.

698
00:39:50,470 --> 00:39:51,710
What kind of person

699
00:39:51,710 --> 00:39:53,780
do you think Mr Zhou Chuan likes?

700
00:39:55,270 --> 00:39:56,150
Chu Li!

701
00:39:57,270 --> 00:40:00,110
What did you say? I wasn't listening.

702
00:40:00,380 --> 00:40:03,710
I was talking about Mr Zhou Chuan.

703
00:40:03,710 --> 00:40:05,030
Why does your laugh

704
00:40:05,190 --> 00:40:07,310
seem so creepy?

705
00:40:07,750 --> 00:40:09,070
Really?

706
00:40:10,030 --> 00:40:10,990
It's nothing.

707
00:40:10,990 --> 00:40:12,380
I just think

708
00:40:12,750 --> 00:40:14,870
that dating isn't a bad thing.

709
00:40:14,870 --> 00:40:16,390
When a guy is dating someone,

710
00:40:16,390 --> 00:40:18,510
he will be more mature.

711
00:40:18,510 --> 00:40:20,110
In that case, he won't give

712
00:40:20,110 --> 00:40:21,590
the editor or art editor a hard time

713
00:40:21,590 --> 00:40:23,510
with his stupid ideas.

714
00:40:23,510 --> 00:40:24,830
Am I right?

715
00:40:25,390 --> 00:40:26,550
No.

716
00:40:26,630 --> 00:40:29,860
I have an evil thought though.

717
00:40:30,190 --> 00:40:32,430
I hope that Mr Zhou Chuan

718
00:40:32,430 --> 00:40:35,140
will break up after one week.

719
00:40:35,260 --> 00:40:36,310
In that case,

720
00:40:36,310 --> 00:40:38,990
he will belong to Chuan's fans club.

721
00:40:38,990 --> 00:40:40,110
You know what?

722
00:40:40,110 --> 00:40:43,180
He lost a lot of readers
after making his relationship public.

723
00:40:46,700 --> 00:40:48,510
I have an announcement to make.

724
00:40:50,310 --> 00:40:51,590
A new colleague

725
00:40:51,590 --> 00:40:53,510
will be joining Yuan Yue Publishing House.

726
00:40:53,710 --> 00:40:55,030
Hi, I'm Zhou Chuan.

727
00:40:55,030 --> 00:40:57,230
I look forward to working with you.

728
00:40:57,670 --> 00:40:59,580
Mr Zhou Chuan's new instalment

729
00:40:59,580 --> 00:41:00,550
is related to editors,

730
00:41:00,550 --> 00:41:02,110
he purposely came to Moonlight Magazine

731
00:41:02,110 --> 00:41:03,310
to gain some experience.

732
00:41:03,830 --> 00:41:04,470
Chu Li,

733
00:41:04,470 --> 00:41:05,270
take him

734
00:41:05,270 --> 00:41:07,550
to get familiar with the environment.

735
00:41:07,550 --> 00:41:09,110
Sure, sure.

736
00:41:20,070 --> 00:41:21,510
Why did you come here all of a sudden?

737
00:41:21,510 --> 00:41:23,270
You didn't even say anything.

738
00:41:23,270 --> 00:41:24,390
I didn't tell you

739
00:41:24,390 --> 00:41:25,950
so that I can give you a surprise.

740
00:41:25,950 --> 00:41:27,150
Are you

741
00:41:27,830 --> 00:41:29,070
not happy?

742
00:41:29,470 --> 00:41:30,550
No.

743
00:41:30,550 --> 00:41:32,140
I was thinking, we can always meet

744
00:41:32,140 --> 00:41:33,750
after work.

745
00:41:33,750 --> 00:41:34,630
Is this because

746
00:41:34,630 --> 00:41:36,030
you miss me so badly

747
00:41:36,030 --> 00:41:38,420
that you have to find an excuse to see me?

748
00:41:38,420 --> 00:41:39,620
You think too much.

749
00:41:39,620 --> 00:41:40,870
I'm preparing

750
00:41:40,870 --> 00:41:43,590
for a modern fantasy novel
related to editors.

751
00:41:43,590 --> 00:41:46,270
Modern fantasy novel?

752
00:41:46,270 --> 00:41:48,870
It doesn't seem legit.

753
00:41:48,870 --> 00:41:51,150
Do you have doubts with my creativity?

754
00:41:51,910 --> 00:41:53,310
Let's drop the new instalments.

755
00:41:53,310 --> 00:41:54,670
No, no!

756
00:41:54,670 --> 00:41:56,070
I was just fooling around.

757
00:41:56,070 --> 00:41:57,390
You're here to gain experience,

758
00:41:57,390 --> 00:42:00,590
you have my full support.

759
00:42:01,070 --> 00:42:03,030
That's more like it.

760
00:42:03,750 --> 00:42:04,750
Then, in the future,

761
00:42:05,070 --> 00:42:06,630
in order to save you some trouble,

762
00:42:06,630 --> 00:42:08,230
since you're here to gain experience,

763
00:42:08,230 --> 00:42:09,310
it is better

764
00:42:09,310 --> 00:42:10,870
if we keep our distance.

765
00:42:10,870 --> 00:42:13,230
If someone knows that we're dating,

766
00:42:13,230 --> 00:42:15,060
people will say
that you're dating your colleague,

767
00:42:15,060 --> 00:42:17,350
your professional image will be affected.

768
00:42:17,350 --> 00:42:18,460
Fine.

769
00:42:18,460 --> 00:42:20,750
So, as not to affect
your professional image as well.

770
00:42:20,750 --> 00:42:21,660
I agree.

771
00:42:22,230 --> 00:42:23,590
When we're in the meeting,

772
00:42:23,590 --> 00:42:24,710
we should sit further from each other.

773
00:42:24,710 --> 00:42:25,510
Keep our distance.

774
00:42:25,510 --> 00:42:26,910
Alright.

775
00:42:30,230 --> 00:42:31,550
However,

776
00:42:33,790 --> 00:42:34,950
since I listen to you,

777
00:42:34,950 --> 00:42:37,310
shouldn't you do something in return?

778
00:42:37,430 --> 00:42:40,390
What should I do?

779
00:42:42,670 --> 00:42:43,310
No.

780
00:42:43,310 --> 00:42:44,550
There are so many people here,

781
00:42:44,550 --> 00:42:46,830
what if they see us?

782
00:42:47,150 --> 00:42:49,500
Then I'll take my words back.

783
00:42:51,470 --> 00:42:52,670
Hurry up. Let's go.
